notesStmt.note: Copy of letter between p. 96-97 in second work is from a French Archbishop to the superior of the French priests at Reading, England and includes the date 31 May 1801.

msContents.summary: Comprised of 2 manuscript works, the first is a copy of a work by John Thayer, originally published in London in 1787, the second is unidentified and has a copy of a letter dated 1801 inserted between p. 96-97; plus 3 printed pamphlets bound in at the end (32 leaves).
